</ul>

<hr />

<h2 id="live-it-out">Live It Out</h2>
<p class="lead">End with a challenge to take action. Choose a closing question to help each person identify their next steps.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Who do you need to confront? How will you prayerfully confront them?</li>
  <li>How can our group pray over these confrontations before they happen?</li>
  <li>What relationship do you need to work to restore?</li>
</ul>
